This is a plugin for bukkit.

AutoShutdown is documented on bukkitdev: http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/autoshutdown/

CHANGELOG:

Version 2.3:

 * Updated to bukkit 1.2.4 (build 1423).
 * Removed the unnecessary server listener. 
 
Version 2.2:

 * Changed to bukkit standard config.yml.
 * Saves new shutdown times when you add them with /as set.
